title: Shoreditch Showdown - Time Lapse
description:
http://www.oneill.com/ridemore
What happens when you dump 50 tonnes of snow in Shoreditch, add a fine sprinkling of iconic London street furniture and invite 24 of the UK's best skiers and snowboarders?! The O'Neill Shoreditch Showdown is what happens... Watch the time-lapse
